</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d259n1-ptr" id="PJA13d259n1">1</a>

   <p>Liges minister at The Hague was Paul Franz von Magis. He presented his credentials in Nov. 1754 and served until Sept. 1788 (<span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Repertorium der diplomatischen Vertreter aller Lnder seit dem Westflischen Frieden (1648&lt;/i&gt;), ed. Ludwig Bittner and others, Oldenburg, &amp;c., 19361965; 3 vols. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Repertorium</span></span>, 3:235).</p>

</div>
